red-Gromov-Hausdorff limit of a sequence of Riemannian\nmanifolds with Ricci curvature bounded from below, showing the consistency of\nour definition with a recent construction of Honda.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Feb 2013 18:22:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-01"}
