 mode space approach is necessary, but the results are still accurate\ncompared to the real-space solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2013 14:07:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2013 22:14:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-12"}
